## Asset Note

Visual assets under `frontend2/public/webtoons/` (covers, avatars, segment
backgrounds, peak close-ups, ending illustrations, splashes, and the oracle
vignette) were generated by an AI image-generation tool. They are released
under the same MIT terms — free to use, modify, and redistribute for any
purpose. No human-authored copyrighted illustration is included.
